To build:
    "make"

To run part I with a varying number of samples and generate images:
    "./run1.sh"

To run part II with a varying number of samples and generate images:
    "./run2.sh"

All data files and images are found in data/.  The power output of every run is found
in data/partX/power, and images are generated using ~7e-16 as the maximum power
at a pixel.

